---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="Get Involved" description="Ways to get involved with the tech community in Hampton Roads.">
  <div class="page-hero">
    <h1>Get Involved</h1>
    <p>There are many ways to contribute to the Hampton Roads tech community.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="sec">ways to participate</div>

  <div class="content-block">
    <h2>Join a Meetup</h2>
    <p>One of the easiest ways to get involved is to join a local meetup group. Check out our <a href="/meetups">Meetups page</a> for a list of active groups. Attend events, network with other professionals, and learn new skills.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="content-block">
    <h2>Join Online Communities</h2>
    <p>Can't make it to in-person events? Join the <a href="https://join.slack.com/t/757dev/shared_invite/zt-37d031yip-yI9z3ez8ezf~mJTy5ICaeQ">757dev Slack</a> or <a href="https://discord.gg/bPGsCKBqWp">Discord</a> to connect with local tech professionals online.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="content-block">
    <h2>Speak at a Meetup</h2>
    <p>Have knowledge to share? Most groups are always looking for speakers. It's a great way to build your personal brand and give back to the community.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="content-block">
    <h2>Organize an Event</h2>
    <p>See a gap in the community? Consider organizing your own event — a workshop, conference, or new meetup group. Not sure if there's enough interest? Try hosting a session with <a href="https://www.meetup.com/757dev/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">757 Developers</a> first.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="content-block">
    <h2>Volunteer</h2>
    <p>Many tech events need volunteers. It's a great way to meet people and contribute. Reach out to event organizers to see how you can help.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="content-block">
    <h2>Mentor Others</h2>
    <p>Share your experience by mentoring others — through formal programs or just being available to answer questions for those starting out.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="content-block">
    <h2>Support Local Organizations</h2>
    <p>Organizations like <a href="https://revolutionva.org">RevolutionVA</a> are working to support and grow the tech community. Consider donating or volunteering.</p>
  </div>
</MainLayout>
